Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.27,0:00:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛馳的秒針 閃耀的流星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.94,0:00:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現代社會人心貧瘠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.85,0:00:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南的推理是一帖良藥喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.61,0:00:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天故事的舞臺是大豪宅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.23,0:00:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的勁敵平次也十分活躍喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.06,0:00:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.69,0:00:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.67,0:00:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.80,0:00:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.31,0:01:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名門連續慘死事件(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.69,0:01:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好氣派的房子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.44,0:01:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是與園子家比肩的長門集團會長的房子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.10,0:01:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳認識園子大小姐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.93,0:02:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她小時候到這裡來過兩三次呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.26,0:02:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她哪有大家閨秀的氣質啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.99,0:02:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼厲害的人找爸爸有什麼事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.63,0:02:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長親自點名找我名偵探毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.33,0:02:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是要我處理什麼疑難案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.66,0:02:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許不過是外遇調查吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.18,0:02:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你胡說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.09,0:02:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.95,0:02:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.34,0:02:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水池邊上怎麼會有這些坑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.15,0:02:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為準備下個星期在這裡種些新的樹木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.11,0:02:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請允許我自我介紹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.64,0:02:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是從前代會長時開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.18,0:02:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一直擔任管家的武藏之介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.45,0:02:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面也好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.01,0:02:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們老爺正在三樓恭候各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.64,0:02:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這麼多警備人員啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.34,0:02:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.34,0:02:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰到棘手案子了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.35,0:02:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.16,0:02:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人好像在哪裡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.41,0:03:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我名偵探毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.53,0:03:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫您尋找初戀女友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.40,0:03:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的老朋友力薦說如果是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.35,0:03:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能在轉瞬之間把人找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.20,0:03:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是尋人這種事情 不必我親自出馬吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.55,0:03:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜 不是疑難案件呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.16,0:03:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那您有那位女士的照片什麽的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.86,0:03:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是小學生的時候 沒留下什麼照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.74,0:03:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連她長什麼樣子都不記得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.49,0:03:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可這段時間不知怎的 總是想起她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.55,0:03:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是個可愛的人兒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.26,0:03:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過世的老婆聽到這些 一定會埋怨我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.08,0:03:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒有照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.80,0:03:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是知道她的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.10,0:03:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及在那以後她的一些消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.71,0:03:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向 拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.85,0:04:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位女士名叫赤城琴美 神奈川縣人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.01,0:04:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中畢業之後在29歲時結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.00,0:04:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她與先生大和行平生了一個小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.90,0:04:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是五年後 三個人卻突然一起失蹤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.18,0:04:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是躲起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.08,0:04:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.03,0:04:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說是誰啊 向您介紹我的那位老朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.15,0:04:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.87,0:04:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.38,0:04:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是我剛才說的那位老朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.15,0:04:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大阪府警察局局長服部平藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.12,0:04:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大阪府警察局局長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.39,0:04:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是每次大阪發生大案時經常在電視上露面的那位…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.18,0:04:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說看起來眼熟嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.92,0:04:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 等一下 就是說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.53,0:04:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 工藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.02,0:04:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近來好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.48,0:04:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服部平次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.00,0:04:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“工藤”…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.71,0:04:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 還沒露餡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.63,0:04:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了 笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.54,0:04:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的“工藤”難道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.42,0:04:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}工藤（くどう）與辛苦（くろう）發音相近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.42,0:04:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的是“辛苦”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.36,0:04:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是辛苦你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.96,0:05:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有客人啊 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.10,0:05:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀…不光是客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.15,0:05:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還混進一隻狐狸精呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.27,0:05:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳最近好像都留宿在這裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.57,0:05:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼迷了妳的心竅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.60,0:05:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.86,0:05:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 信子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.80,0:05:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這樣動不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.41,0:05:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了報告公司的各項決定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.79,0:05:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事用傳真就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.59,0:05:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那麽多事情…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.47,0:05:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的幾位又是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.32,0:05:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.70,0:05:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵…偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.85,0:05:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵探怎麼會來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.81,0:05:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長爲了尋找初戀情人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.35,0:05:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以請他們來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.40,0:05:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.97,0:05:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種髒兮兮的鋼筆還拿著哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.36,0:05:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是不是你爸爸的遺物 不過一看就令人噁心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.22,0:05:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,康江妳不小心一點的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.07,0:05:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳最重要的光明就要被人家勾走了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.30,0:06:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.45,0:06:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.87,0:06:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊 日向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.62,0:06:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信子因為到了那個年紀婚事還沒有著落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.55,0:06:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以心情烦躁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.85,0:06:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.65,0:06:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她那樣子一輩子都沒希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.78,0:06:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我回公司一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.77,0:06:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.85,0:06:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算今晚就向大家公佈那件事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.60,0:06:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你還同情我兒子的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.65,0:06:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什麽同情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.01,0:06:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和他命中注定如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.55,0:06:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從很久以前 就被火燄的紐帶聯結在一起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.93,0:06:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“火燄的紐帶”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.67,0:06:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們原來是劍道部的學長和學弟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.72,0:06:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長門兄以前像凶神一般 把我們整得好慘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.55,0:06:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 平藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.93,0:06:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次那件事情…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.23,0:06:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經派警員去查了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.84,0:07:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.11,0:07:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我兒子秀臣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.84,0:07:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讀高中的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.09,0:07:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一場意外中臉部被嚴重燒傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.82,0:07:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後就一直這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.08,0:07:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依靠如今的整形技術 我想多少可以改善吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.75,0:07:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他自己不願意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.42,0:07:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.47,0:07:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那次事件開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.91,0:07:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才有如今圓滿的結局呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.29,0:07:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀臣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.32,0:07:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀臣 等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.03,0:07:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你生什麼氣嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.95,0:07:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.94,0:07:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝您生日快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.29,0:07:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.73,0:07:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果作爲報答 您肯儘快將會長寶座讓給我的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.50,0:07:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會很開心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.98,0:07:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的啦 開玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.70,0:07:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也該回大阪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.89,0:08:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今晚不留下來為我慶生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.03,0:08:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有之前那件事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.47,0:08:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.15,0:08:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我留下這小子代替我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.23,0:08:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看他還年輕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.28,0:08:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可用心的時候也蠻機靈的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.13,0:08:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一定能幫上毛利偵探的忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.58,0:08:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫忙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.80,0:08:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快樂 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.87,0:08:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快樂 老爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.57,0:08:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實呢 有件事情想借這個機會告訴大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.42,0:08:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬子秀臣和日向幸的婚事已經確定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.30,0:08:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎 老爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.04,0:08:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是為了讓阿幸早點習慣這個家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.44,0:08:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才請她住在這裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.19,0:08:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.66,0:08:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信子小姐 妳去哪兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.72,0:08:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.50,0:08:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下仍然單身的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.71,0:08:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只剩她一人而已啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.01,0:09:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 秀臣怎麽還不露面呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.51,0:09:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙一定在害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.55,0:09:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這就把他叫來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.42,0:09:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服部 快說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.38,0:09:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.24,0:09:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.13,0:09:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我們招來這裡 還特意要我們留下的真實原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.78,0:09:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.83,0:09:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不過是想念你罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.53,0:09:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙你的騙你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.51,0:09:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.66,0:09:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.49,0:09:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.37,0:09:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓爸爸聽電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.05,0:09:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…老爺…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.25,0:09:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經睡了 我們也正要離開呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.58,0:09:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀臣不見了 到處都找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.40,0:09:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙究竟在哪裡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.90,0:09:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光明先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.39,0:09:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.43,0:09:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在在哪兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.87,0:09:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在你們正下面的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.43,0:09:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人把燈關了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.68,0:09:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿著刀從後面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.78,0:10:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.19,0:10:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光明先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.45,0:10:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.83,0:10:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光明先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.06,0:10:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是秀臣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.47,0:10:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起去阻止他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.59,0:10:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.66,0:10:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀臣為什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.13,0:10:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 打不開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.73,0:10:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從裡面反鎖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.57,0:10:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我這就去拿備份鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.23,0:10:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.88,0:10:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去和警衛從外面圍堵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.92,0:10:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光…光明 你怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.78,0:10:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.72,0:10:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵探先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.52,0:10:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,備份鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.89,0:10:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.68,0:10:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外面嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.77,0:10:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.52,0:10:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道他利用繩子逃到下面去了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.77,0:10:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是光明在哪兒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.44,0:10:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.10,0:10:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.99,0:11:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被推落到栅欄上面的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.85,0:11:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼是真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.83,0:11:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手是長門先生的兒子秀臣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.78,0:11:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.75,0:11:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手不是秀臣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.08,0:11:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中一定有…有什麼緣故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.47,0:11:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管什麼緣故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.01,0:11:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不都是殺人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.91,0:11:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我 我的光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.47,0:11:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可秀臣不是會做這種事的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.86,0:11:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我們看到的那個人也不一定就是秀臣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.30,0:11:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說得沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.75,0:11:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.85,0:11:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是個臉上纏了繃帶的人而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.15,0:11:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繃帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.25,0:11:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀臣先生的臉曾經被嚴重燒傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.53,0:11:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們看到兇手的時候是晚上十點多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.21,0:11:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時大家剛好都聚集在三樓會長的寢室裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.82,0:11:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“大家”是指…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.33,0:12:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時在會長臥室的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.43,0:12:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我、平次、小蘭、柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.82,0:12:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及管家武先生和康江小姐六個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.38,0:12:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家離開房間以後 妳在做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.91,0:12:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我留在臥室裡陪伴會長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.04,0:12:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是兇手爲了從陽臺逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.26,0:12:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至預先準備了那種帶鉤的繩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.66,0:12:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手使用了那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.51,0:12:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點應該錯不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.86,0:12:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和警衛從外面包抄過來的時候 繩子還在晃呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.52,0:12:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涉嫌的秀臣先生在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.33,0:12:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到處都找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.47,0:12:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在警方各位到達之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.40,0:12:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一直在找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.52,0:12:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼兇手就是秀臣先生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.20,0:12:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.82,0:12:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.01,0:12:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作爲兇器的刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.57,0:12:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及兇手使用的繃帶和帽子都已找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.90,0:12:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加以檢查的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.01,0:12:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右手上的這個傷口是怎麽回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.14,0:12:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被什麼東西刺到造成的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.21,0:13:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正就是被兇手用刀刺的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.91,0:13:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然就是他被推下去以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.44,0:13:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被栅欄的某個地方碰到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.71,0:13:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.10,0:13:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦 高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.89,0:13:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據栅欄外面設置的防盜錄影机的記錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.17,0:13:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有任何人在案發之後離開過這幢房子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.41,0:13:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼兇手…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.37,0:13:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在房子裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.88,0:13:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.11,0:13:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長現在應該…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.66,0:13:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 會長他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.24,0:13:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 門鎖著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.57,0:13:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 有人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.77,0:13:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.84,0:13:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都聚在這裡幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.54,0:13:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麽會在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.84,0:13:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽見周圍亂哄哄的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.54,0:13:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心不下就來到這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.67,0:13:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這裡之前妳在什麼地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.93,0:13:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心中煩悶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.46,0:13:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在自己房間裡喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.21,0:13:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.32,0:14:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還一邊給朋友打電話發牢騷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.59,0:14:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過因為喝酒的關係 都不記得打給誰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.21,0:14:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來是真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.86,0:14:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀臣殺了光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.88,0:14:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.11,0:14:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.46,0:14:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早覺得他有一天會這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.47,0:14:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.87,0:14:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次碰面都要大吵一架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.07,0:14:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是從小的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.59,0:14:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前好像感情還不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.30,0:14:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可從那件事情之後就水火不容了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.17,0:14:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“那件事情”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.82,0:14:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.86,0:14:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二十年前這裡附近的一家旅館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.33,0:14:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經發生過一場大火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.05,0:14:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.33,0:14:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同是高中生的秀臣和光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.44,0:14:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那裡經過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.20,0:14:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛管閒事的秀臣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.19,0:14:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掙脫光明的阻攔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.39,0:14:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝入火海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.37,0:14:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救出一名不及逃出的少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.29,0:14:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這位日向幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.21,0:14:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.41,0:14:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以是“火燄的紐帶”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.18,0:14:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀臣因此臉部被嚴重燒傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.55,0:15:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那天開始 秀臣學校也不去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.25,0:15:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落得成天窩在屋裡 充什麽小說家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.75,0:15:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然身旁也沒有一個女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.35,0:15:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個女人就藉此接近秀臣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.28,0:15:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他推薦自己做爸爸的秘書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.09,0:15:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至妄想和他結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.75,0:15:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說了 信子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.42,0:15:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.09,0:15:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.66,0:15:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直就是半睡半醒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.62,0:15:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從你們大家吵吵嚷嚷地離開這房間的時候開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.20,0:15:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後 有沒有什麼奇怪的事情發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.03,0:15:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.80,0:15:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在小蘭過來以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.09,0:15:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向小姐一直都陪在我身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.72,0:15:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 現在恐怕不是尋找您初戀情人的時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.58,0:15:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事就算了 把它忘了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.14,0:15:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不說叫我來這裡的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.09,0:16:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.26,0:16:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實呢 長門會長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.86,0:16:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天夜裡聽到了奇怪的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.02,0:16:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.26,0:16:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人半夜在走廊裡噼嗒噼嗒的跑步聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.85,0:16:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有好幾次什麽東西相撞的怪聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.17,0:16:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.84,0:16:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.09,0:16:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是這家裡的某人在為這次的謀殺進行準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.92,0:16:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來我和老爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.55,0:16:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都以為不過是小偷預先探路之類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.77,0:16:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以出動警力 還招來你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.61,0:16:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心想小偷今晚一定會來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.15,0:16:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻沒想到拿走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.37,0:16:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是條人命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.57,0:16:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預謀殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.57,0:16:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你不覺得奇怪嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.59,0:16:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有拜你所賜而聲名大噪的毛利小五郎坐鎮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.30,0:16:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來兇手對自己的殺人計劃相當自信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.65,0:16:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.98,0:16:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計劃已經無法變更了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.47,0:17:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的是兇手掉在屍體附近的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.51,0:17:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺留物品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.57,0:17:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇器倒沒什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.99,0:17:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但既然要迅速逃跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.46,0:17:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大可不必還脫下帽子和繃帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.11,0:17:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且兇手特意向我們展示他的臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.04,0:17:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯然是要嫁禍於秀臣先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.39,0:17:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 可能做到這些的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.56,0:17:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有中途離開寢室的信子小姐一個人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.59,0:17:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.59,0:17:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家用了一天一夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.96,0:17:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把房子裡面所有角落統統搜查了一遍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.97,0:17:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻都沒有秀臣先生的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.87,0:17:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警方與我們都已經要放棄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.46,0:17:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案發後第二天的傍晚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.19,0:17:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 警官 哪兒都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.71,0:17:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.29,0:17:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀臣沒有結婚是因爲我的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.19,0:17:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.13,0:17:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說秀臣是因為顧及到我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.47,0:17:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我只是說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.35,0:17:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他肯為姐姐著想 是個體貼的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.05,0:17:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.80,0:17:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.37,0:18:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要下去 這個水池很深的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.22,0:18:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那支鋼筆是爸爸的遺物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.58,0:18:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒了的話 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.62,0:18:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把水放掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.22,0:18:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我這就去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.00,0:18:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真髒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.60,0:18:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前夫人在這裡養過鯉魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.77,0:18:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她去世以後…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.45,0:18:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.78,0:18:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.10,0:18:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.34,0:18:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀臣哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.02,0:18:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀臣先生推定的死亡時間是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.83,0:18:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該已經死亡約一天半到兩天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.78,0:18:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光明先生從陽臺上被推下去的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.97,0:18:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是前天晚上十點鐘左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.87,0:18:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是距離現在四十四個小時之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.01,0:18:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如秀臣先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.25,0:19:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我們到達這裡之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.08,0:19:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於這個水池投水自殺的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.83,0:19:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切就都吻合了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.68,0:19:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是死因並不是溺水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.90,0:19:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然未經解剖不能斷定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.43,0:19:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他應該是服毒之後才跳進水池的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.22,0:19:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍體沒有浮上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.95,0:19:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為衣服裡面裝了這些石頭的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.78,0:19:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼秀臣先生是帶著石頭跳進水池
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.81,0:19:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服毒自殺的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.89,0:19:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定是不想被人看到自己的死狀吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.59,0:19:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.12,0:19:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀臣先生和光明先生之間關係再惡劣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.89,0:19:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不至於殺人吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.06,0:19:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也許是因為秀臣少爺跟康江小姐感情特別好的緣故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.87,0:19:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於康江小姐和光明先生的婚事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.45,0:19:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直堅持反對的人就是秀臣少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.24,0:19:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是珍愛的妹妹被自己憎惡的朋友得到 心中不平吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.69,0:20:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻孩子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.24,0:20:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目暮警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.31,0:20:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑑定的結果出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.29,0:20:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,念來聽聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.89,0:20:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在現場發現的菜刀刀刃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.18,0:20:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與光明先生手腕的傷口吻合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.70,0:20:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜刀上附著的鮮血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.46,0:20:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也確定是光明先生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.78,0:20:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.68,0:20:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與菜刀散落在一起的帽子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.08,0:20:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和繃帶上沾附的毛髮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.85,0:20:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是秀臣先生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.64,0:20:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 光明先生的上衣兜裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.84,0:20:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有條長約一公尺的風箏線…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.04,0:20:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風箏線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.77,0:20:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右手手背上的傷口也是刀傷嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.60,0:20:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點不太一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.70,0:20:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜刀上應該沾有唾液 是什麽血型的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.63,0:20:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有唾液啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.45,0:20:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是被擦掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.30,0:20:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.01,0:20:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者口袋裡有這樣一張紙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.52,0:20:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有資格和你結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.66,0:20:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了彌補我犯下的罪過 我選擇死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.28,0:20:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是遺書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.40,0:21:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸小姐 是給妳的遺書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.36,0:21:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是秀臣先生的字嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.63,0:21:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.35,0:21:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去秀臣的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.51,0:21:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿些他寫的東西過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.60,0:21:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸小姐 這…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.02,0:21:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妳掉到水池裡的鋼筆…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.16,0:21:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.95,0:21:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吵她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.79,0:21:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那支鋼筆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.99,0:21:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下我交給她好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.82,0:21:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀臣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.27,0:21:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這支鋼筆給燒得真厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.77,0:21:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.14,0:21:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.96,0:21:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件案子的確是莫名其妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.14,0:21:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最不自然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.64,0:21:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那封遺書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.74,0:21:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺書中說“我犯下的罪過”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.57,0:21:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽應該是他殺掉光明先生以後寫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.71,0:21:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可他怎麼會在那種時候 還去悠閒地寫什麽遺書呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.89,0:21:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 那封遺書是有人脅迫他寫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.26,0:21:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是偽造的
